thread.title: BRIEF-Moneysupermarket.com Group's chief product officer to leave
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Moneysupermarket.com Group's chief product officer to leave | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Moneysupermarket.com Group's chief product officer to leave
text:
Oct 8 Moneysupermarket.Com Group Plc :
* Graham Donoghue, chief product officer, has decided to step out of business
* Donoghue will leave board now but will remain with company until end of year
* Donoghue's successor has already been identified Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Bengaluru Newsroom: +91 80 6749 1136)
